Package: germlinevaR
Title: End-to-End Germline VCF Analysis, Filtering and Visualisation
Version: 0.99.2
Date: 2026-07-02
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Thiago", "Loreto Matos",
             email   = "thiago-loreto@hotmail.com",
